<view class="page qimen-page">
  <x-pattern />

  <view class="tool-title-hero">
    <view class="tool-title">奇门</view>
    <view class="tool-subtitle">时空起局 · 九宫研判</view>
    <view class="tool-stamp">起局</view>
  </view>

  <view class="section input-panel">
    <view class="section-kicker">一事一局</view>
    <view class="section-title">问事与起局</view>
    <view class="qimen-form-list">
      <view class="qimen-setting-row qimen-question-row">
        <text class="qimen-setting-label">事项内容</text>
        <textarea placeholder="请输入事项（选填）" value="{{form.question}}" bindinput="onQuestionInput" />
      </view>
      <view class="qimen-setting-row">
        <text class="qimen-setting-label">排盘时间</text>
        <view class="qimen-time-value" bindtap="useCurrentTime">
          <text>{{form.date}} {{form.time}}</text>
          <text class="time-refresh">↻</text>
        </view>
      </view>
      <view
        class="qimen-setting-row qimen-option-row"
        wx:for="{{qimenRows}}"
        wx:for-item="row"
        wx:for-index="rowIndex"
        wx:key="key"
      >
        <text class="qimen-setting-label">{{row.label}}</text>
        <view class="qimen-radio-group">
          <view
            class="qimen-radio {{option.active ? 'active' : ''}}"
            wx:for="{{row.options}}"
            wx:for-item="option"
            wx:key="value"
            bindtap="onQimenOptionTap"
            data-key="{{row.key}}"
            data-value="{{option.value}}"
          >
            <text class="radio-dot">{{option.active ? '✓' : ''}}</text>
            <text>{{option.value}}</text>
          </view>
        </view>
      </view>
    </view>
    <view class="ritual-panel">
      <view class="ritual-title">起局前</view>
      <view class="ritual-row">
        <text class="ritual-dot"></text>
        <text>一事一局，先把问题写具体，不混问多个方向。</text>
      </view>
      <view class="ritual-row">
        <text class="ritual-dot"></text>
        <text>奇门重时空，测试版会保留起局时间方便后续复盘。</text>
      </view>
    </view>
    <button class="primary" bindtap="generateChart">生成奇门局</button>
  </view>
</view>
